<figureCitation box="[820,887,449,472]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="6.[136,171,2065,2086]" captionText="Fig. 4. Map showing distribution of P. brachysoma, P. longipterus and P. yunnanensis." pageId="5" pageNumber="152">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
